                <h2>1. Southwest Airlines Pet Policy – In-Cabin Travel</h2>
                <p>The airline only allows small pets in the cabin and does not permit the animals to travel in the cargo hold. Therefore, if you are flying with a pet, here are the key things to know: the allowed pets, pet carrier requirement, weight limit, and the number of pets. We classify each thing very simply.</p>
